CLOSE TO EVERYTHING!

The single level home offers sunny, open plan living/dining area with a modern kitchen plus an additional family room.

With the added convenience of low maintenance landscaped gardens this neat property requires nothing but your family to move in and enjoy or is the perfect location for a holiday getaway.

QUIET LOCATION
This lovely established home, is situated on a corner allotment, in a quiet cul-de-sac, only a few minutes' drive from central Cowes and only a short walk to the beach. The established gardens give the home a cottage charm that makes you feel at ease the moment you enter the property. Partly renovated, and separated into two zones this home offers itself to a variety of uses, whether for extended family use, or even to continue the current owner's Air BnB business. Consisting of 2 double bedrooms, third bedroom currently being used as a second living area , kitchen & kitchenette, and large family bathroom, as well as a separate studio with reverse cycle air conditioning & bathroom. Cathedral ceilings, timber veneer flooring, wood heater, reverse cycle air conditioning, plus ceiling fans in the bedrooms are just some of the additional features that this home offers. With 3 vehicle access points via the two street frontages, there is plenty of room for extra cars, a boat or caravan. The possibilities are endless.

Description:
BRAND NEW FOUR BEDROOM HOME - CORNER BLOCK NORTHERLY ASPECT
Only moments from the majestic Cowes foreshore, eateries, various clubs and golfcourses, this gorgeous property with all facilities at its door step and the added benefit of a professionally landscaped courtyards and gardens, is the one you have been waiting for….. This is a quality 'BRAND NEW' 4 Bedroom, 6.5 start energy rated brick home with double garage on an above average wide block corner constructed by one of Melbourne's leading and most reputable builders. As you walk into this home you will instantly feel the abundance of space and be inundated by natural light radiating throughout the kitchen, dining and main living areas. The master bedroom/ parents retreat is huge with a full walk in wardrobe and personal ensuite, with double shower…. additionally the 3 large extra bedrooms give you plenty of room for your family and friends. The 1st living space adjoins the large hostess kitchen with stone bench tops, boasting quality 900m stainless appliances which open up to a large rear courtyard. The second living space provides a separate zone which can be used as a living/rumpus/ entertainment room, or even an office. The north facing courtyard fronting the kitchen area is ideal for that morning coffee and catching up on the daily news with an unobstructed view of the tree tops and horizon. This home also provides you with the benefits of a second driveway, with ample room to store your boat/caravan or trailer behind securely closed gates.
A very special aspect of this unique home is the corner location with a true unobstructed northerly aspect throughout all the living, dining, rumpus and kitchen areas. Surrounded by nature parks, wetlands, fishing spots, and walking tracks…. Your brand new, fully landscaped home is ready for you to move in……
Inspection highly recommended.

Description:
Position Perfect!
This lovely double story residence is situated on a large 910 sqm (approx) allotment in a quiet pocket of Cowes, close to shops, schools and easy walking distance to Thompson Avenue.
The ground level is the heart of the home, with open plan living, kitchen and dining. The spacious kitchen is complemented by gas cooktop, electric wall oven and a two drawer dishwasher. Also on this level is the master suite, with ensuite and built in robe, a good sized family bathroom and laundry. A rumpus or extra living area with its own bar / kitchenette is at the rear of the home, which leads out to an undercover entertaining area, with cafe blinds for year round use, and an outdoor spa.
On the upper level of the home is a further 2 bedrooms with built in robes, living area and expansive north facing balcony - perfect spot for catching the morning sun with a cup of coffee! Another family bathroom completes this level.
The huge fully fenced rear yard has a large double garage (approx 6m x 10m) which has plenty of room for a workshop, garden tools etc. There is also an additional storage shed at the side of the property.
Other features include:- Split system heating and cooling upstairs, gas ducted heating / cooling downstairs
This Cowes property is proudly presented by Ray White Real Estate Phillip Island.

Description:
JUST BEAUTIFUL
Walk to everything from this perfectly located home in central Cowes.
This beautiful residence has all the charm and character of a period style, however has all the comforts a modern home.
Behind the charming facade is a tastefully renovated and stunning home. The three beautifully appointed bedrooms feature built in robes and high ceilings throughout which are also serviced by a large central bathroom and separate toilet.
The home features generous living spaces with separate lounge flowing through to the kitchen and dining; all opening onto a sunny, north facing deck through french doors.
The backyard is large and also has a double garage and even a cubby house.This home is a must inspect.
